{
  "message": "chore(supply-chain): bump browser package versions, regenerate integrity docs\n\nUpdated package.json versions across the browser package family\n(browser-core, browser, next, react) to reflect the new v1 ABI export\nimplementation.  Regenerated the three supply-chain verification\ndocuments:\n\n- artifact_integrity_manifest_v1.json: updated SHA-256 digests for all\n  changed package manifests and source files\n- provenance_attestation_v1.json: refreshed per-artifact digests to\n  match the new content hashes\n- sbom_v1.json: updated component checksums\n\nThese documents track the content-addressable identity of every shipped\nartifact so downstream consumers can verify nothing was tampered with\nbetween build and distribution.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>",
